text: hey it's angel today I'm making my
homemade version of a Chinese takeout
soup so if you guys like a flower or egg
drop soup this is my version of the soup
using sweet corn now I love this recipe
because it literally only takes five
minutes to make and if I'm making a
family-style meal and I feel like I just
need a little something extra to make
the meal complete this is my go-to soup
recipe just because it's so quick and
easy and it's delicious so if this
sounds like soup for you keep watching
for the tuskegee we'll need a few simple
ingredients we'll start with some
low-sodium chicken broth bonus points if
you guys have your own chicken stock on
hand homemade is that what's the best
we'll also need one can of whole kernel
sweet corn now try and find the kind
that has no salt added because we'll be
using some of this liquid in our recipe
we'll also need two tablespoons of corn
starch to thicken our soup one egg
slightly beaten and finally some
scallions for garnish now let's prepare
our soup start with your can of sweet
corn and drain half the liquid leaving
roughly half to use in our soup to make
this recipe easier and for less cleanup
I'm going to use the same can to measure
out one and a half cans of chicken stock
add the broth directly to your pot then
let's head over to the stove to cook
heat up the soup and while you're
waiting for it to boil
prepare the cornstarch by dissolving it
in a small amount of cold water and if
you haven't done so already lightly beat
one egg in a small bowl once the soup
has come to a boil stir then add in your
egg mixture let it sit for a few seconds
to cook then stir again to break up the
egg and watch it turn into a pretty
flower like pattern hence the name egg
flower soup after that add in your corn
starch mixture and stir quickly to
thicken the soup once it's thickened add
in some salt and a few dashes of white
pepper to taste then turn off the heat
and serve the soup family-style
garnished with some fresh scallions
so this is how you make my home a
version of a Chinese egg drop soup so if
you guys are Chinese takeout I'm sure
you'll love my healthy version of this
homemade classic thank you guys so much
for watching I hope you enjoyed my quick
and easy soup tutorial give me a thumbs
up if you did and I will see you guys
next time bye
